MQuLz4mi224.title: Satisfactory Alpha Gameplay! Locating the 'Cube Base' Site | Season 1 Ep 1
MQuLz4mi224.description:
So I decided to finally edit a video I made on the Alpha weekend and make a little Satisfactory series.

It's enjoying for me to try a game like this and record it for some reason, I hope anyone that watches enjoys it too.

Things I plan to do in the future of this series:
Giant Cube Base (obviously) - I wanna be really artistic with this game and try to make a huge mega factory and constantly optimise it, and expand it as new updates come. This is going to be the highlight of the series and I can't wait to find a good place to build it!

If logic gates are ever a thing, and maybe programmable lights, I **have** to carry on the tradition I started of making lamp signs in Satisfactory as well as Factorio, I really hope something like that is added; would be so fun to decorate my base with them!
